title: The List with Colleen Lopez 09.07.2017 - 9 PM
description:
Special host, Amy Morrison is taking us through the hottest items for fall featuring Dolce Vita, Vince Camuto, Steve Madden, and more!  The List takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.

Watch every Thursday at 9 pm ET. *Prices shown on the previously recorded video may not represent the current price. Visit http://www.hsn.com to view the current selling price.
